<p style="Normal" xid="145" props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:ru-RU; margin-bottom:0.1944in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; text-align:left; line-height:1.000000; font-size:12pt"><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">I completed the</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; dir-override:ltr; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"> </c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">720</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; dir-override:ltr; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"> </c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">hour course with welding certifications in SMAW(stick</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; dir-override:ltr; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">)</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">,GTAW(TIG or heliarc</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; dir-override:ltr; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">)</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">,</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; dir-override:ltr; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"> </c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">and GMAW(MIG</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; dir-override:ltr; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">) </c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">processes of welding</c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; dir-override:ltr; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">; </c><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none">in both structural and pipe.</c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="146" props="font-family:Times New Roman; dom-dir:ltr; font-style:normal; margin-left:0.0000in; lang:ru-RU; margin-bottom:0.0000in; text-indent:0.0000in; text-position:normal; margin-top:0.0000in; font-weight:normal; margin-right:0.0000in; text-decoration:none; text-align:left; line-height:1.000000; font-size:12pt"><c props="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:12pt; lang:ru-RU; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; text-decoration:none"></c><image dataid="5" xid="148" props="height:0.020833in; width:6.000000in"/></p>
